{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲与徐子陵在山野间赶路时发现一座被焚毁的小镇，镇内百姓惨遭屠戮。两人追上撤退的隋军败兵，在骡车上发现被奸杀的民女残骸。寇仲与徐子陵怒而出手，杀死作恶的隋兵老张及其同伙。随后两人循喊杀声赶到战场，发现一支穿着青色劲装的义军正在与近万隋兵鏖战。二人以树干为兵器冲入敌阵，在生死关头将九玄大法、长生诀、血战十式和鸟渡术融会贯通，创出独有战法，成功杀出重围。休整后，两人毅然决定再次前往战场支援义军，展现了从街头混混到行侠仗义的转变。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "那是甚么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "火！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们快去看看！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_che_sui_bing",
      "speaker_name": "驾车隋兵",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang",
      "text": "老张你真行，这是第三个了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "老张",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死剩种，是你们的娘给我干了吗？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "快溜！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我刚杀了人呢！怎想得到一脚就会把他踢死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这种杀人放火，奸淫妇女之徒，死不足惜，何用心内不安。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们扬州城内的狗兵那个不是横行不法，欺压良民，只想不到连杀人放火都是他们的杰作，难怪这么多人作反了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "比起上来，老爹的手下算是不错了。咦！你听到甚么声音吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "早知把刚才那枝长矛检来，就可去找那些狗兵拚命了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们先去看清楚情况，要抢两把刀还不容易，横竖我们最缺乏就是打斗的经验，就拿这些禽兽不如的贼兵来试刀好了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "看来我们现在颇有两下子，只是没有机会多作演练尝试，兄弟！来吧！今日就是我们纵横江湖开始的第一天了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "那可能是另一个乡县，说不定青衣武士这一方正阻止隋兵到那去杀人放火，这究竟是甚么一回事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若这是老爹方面的人，我们就不宜插手，否则岂非送自己入虎口吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "老爹的手下那有这么衣服划一整齐的，看来该是另一支义军。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "嘿！小陵！你是否胆怯了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "行侠仗义，升官发财，全靠这家伙了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "徐壮士请先行！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "风萧萧兮逆水寒，壮士一去兮定要还。哈！老子去了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "到石上去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们闯！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "哈！成功了！这么大阵仗都杀不死我们，你以前有想过吗？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "刚才我们那种打法太用力了，其实在这情况下可多保留点力气，就不用像现在那么手软脚软了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你有受伤吗？我的背被人砍了两刀，幸好我闪避得快。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "只是左腿处给矛刃擦破了裤子，不算甚么。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "还打不打，那些义军似乎不像表面的风光呢！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当然打，若教这些不是人的隋军攻入那条村庄或墟镇，又会发生像刚才的可怕情况了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这才是我的好兄弟，今次我们放聪明点，不要半途就给人截着了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    }
  ],
